    <p>Snoze your break?</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Enforce break with concrete endtime</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Get into flow and donâ€™t take a break</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Meditation? Meditate on what Iâ€™m going to do?</p>
